  job when reading from one autochanger and writing to another.
  Testing is needed.
  Apply this patch to Bacula version 2.4.2 with:

  cd <bacula-source>
  patch -p0 <2.4.2-inchanger.patch
  ./configure <your options>
  make
  ...
  make install


